2025-09-02 09:08:52.230 +03:30 [Information] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command.) Executed DbCommand ("26"ms) [Parameters=["@__UserId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32)"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[EntityId], [c0].[Text], CASE
    WHEN [c0].[Name] IS NULL OR [c0].[Name] LIKE N'' THEN [m].[FullName]
    ELSE [c0].[Name]
END AS [Name], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[IsApproved], [c0].[EntityType]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[EntityId], [c].[EntityType], [c].[IsApproved], [c].[Name], [c].[Text], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [dbo].[Comments] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[UserId] <> @__UserId_0 OR [c].[UserId] IS NULL
    ORDER BY [c].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [c0]
